@baseUrl = https://localhost:7293

### Test Search and Filter Functionality

### 1. Search by Keyword - "C#"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=C%23&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 2. Search by Keyword - "SQL"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=SQL&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 3. Filter by Category - Lập trình C# (ID = 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdDanhMuc=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 4. Filter by Category - Cơ sở dữ liệu (ID = 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdDanhMuc=2&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 5. Filter by Difficulty - "Dễ"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?DoKho=Dễ&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 6. Filter by Difficulty - "Trung bình"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?DoKho=Trung%20bình&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 7. Filter by Department - "CNTT"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?KhoaPhong=CNTT&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 8. Filter by Question Type - Trắc nghiệm (ID = 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdLoaiCauHoi=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 9. Combined Filters - Category + Difficulty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdDanhMuc=1&DoKho=Dễ&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 10. Combined Filters - Category + Department + Difficulty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdDanhMuc=1&KhoaPhong=CNTT&DoKho=Dễ&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 11. Search + Filter - Keyword + Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=class&IdDanhMuc=1&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 12. Pagination Test - Page 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?PageNumber=1&PageSize=3
Accept: application/json

### 13. Pagination Test - Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?PageNumber=2&PageSize=3
Accept: application/json

### 14. Large Page Size Test
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?PageSize=100
Accept: application/json

### 15. Invalid Page Number (should return empty or error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?PageNumber=999&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 16. Search with Special Characters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=ASP.NET&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 17. Search with No Results
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=NonExistentKeyword&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 18. Filter with Invalid Category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?IdDanhMuc=999&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 19. Empty Search (should return all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 20. Case Insensitive Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cauhoi?SearchKeyword=constructor&PageSize=10
Accept: application/json